OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,GNobody ever likes to see prices go up.
OL,8,FBut the #5 rise in the TV Licence
OL,9,Fshould be welcomed by all who care
OL,10,Fabout public service broadcasting.
OL,12,FConfirmation the licence would rise in
OL,13,Fline with inflation for the next three
OL,14,Fyears came on Friday.
OL,16,FIt was, perhaps, a day to bury what
OL,17,Fsome of the press might interpret as
OL,18,F"bad" news. The news agenda was
OL,19,Fdominated by the momentous decision on
OL,20,Fassisted dying in England and Wales.
