OL,6,FUndoubtedly this meant there was less
OL,7,Fcriticism on Saturday than you might
OL,8,Fhave expected from the usual suspects
OL,9,Fin the parts of the press which are no
OL,10,Ffriends of the BBC.
OL,12,FThe TV Licence, after the rise, will
OL,13,Fcost 48p per day.
OL,15,FIt is not hard to argue that it
OL,16,Frepresents excellent value for money
OL,17,Fif you enjoy or appreciate BBC
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,20,FYou'd be doing well to buy a decent
OL,21,Fcoffee for less than #3. The Sunday
OL,22,FTimes costs #4.50.
