OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FFor some this may be a simple matter
OL,7,Fof taste and preference ` others may
OL,8,Fhave more malign reasons, a belief
OL,9,Fthat BBC journalism is biased or a
OL,10,Fdislike of the corporation's core
OL,11,Fvalues.
OL,13,FIt was ever thus. Is this really any
OL,14,Fdifferent to the household in the 70s
OL,15,Fwhich kept the TV almost permanently
OL,16,Fon ITV?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/12
