OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FStill the BBC is paid for by every
OL,7,Fhonest person in the country with a TV
OL,8,Fset so it should always be a concern
OL,9,Fif someone is paying for something
OL,10,Fthey do not use. (What about those who
OL,11,Fdon't have a TV but watch online?)
OL,13,FThat does not necessarily imply that
OL,14,Fprogrammes or key services need to
OL,15,Fchange. The challenge is to help make
OL,16,Fsure people know about the content
OL,17,Fthey might enjoy.
OL,19,FFriday's rise is a welcome sign that
OL,20,Fthe new government accepts the
OL,21,Fimportance of the BBC to both society
OL,22,Fas a whole and creative industries.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/12
