OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FGiven the cuts to commissioning
OL,7,Fbudgets in the commercial sector, the
OL,8,Farguments for ensuring the BBC is
OL,9,Fproperly funded are stronger than ever.
OL,11,FMeanwhile there is renewed speculation
OL,12,Fabout an overseas takeover bid for ITV
OL,13,Fplc. This too only strengthens the
OL,14,Fargument that a publicly owned
OL,15,Fcorporation must be at the heart of
OL,16,Fbroadcasting.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/12
