OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,F(The threat of privatising Channel 4
OL,7,Fhas gone for now but, as I have said
OL,8,Fbefore, Channel 4 really needs to
OL,9,Fdemonstrate that it is different to
OL,10,Fthe other commercial channels if it
OL,11,Fwants to ensure the issue is not
OL,12,Fraised again.)
OL,14,FBut while Friday's announcement on BBC
OL,15,Ffunding was good news, there are still
OL,16,Fimportant issues to consider.
OL,18,FIt will hopefully mitigate further
OL,19,Fcuts. But it comes after years of
OL,20,Flicence fee freezes and rises which
OL,21,Ffell below inflation.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/12
