OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FThis, of course, has meant cuts. Some
OL,7,Fof those cuts have had a real impact
OL,8,Fon staff not to mention important
OL,9,Fservices like the BBC News channel.
OL,11,FThere will always be legitimate
OL,12,Fquestions over how money is spent `
OL,13,Fmore for this service, less for that
OL,14,Fone. But let's hope the need for
OL,15,Fheadline cuts is over.
OL,17,FThere must also be a debate over
OL,18,Falternatives to the licence fee ` so
OL,19,Flong as this does not mean
OL,20,Fsubscription, commercial funding or
OL,21,Fdirect government funding.
