OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FIs there an argument for a household
OL,7,Fcharge instead? Or linking it to, say,
OL,8,Fcouncil tax bands so there might be
OL,9,Fsome relationship to wealth?
OL,11,FBringing back universal free TV
OL,12,Flicences for the elderly could help
OL,13,Fcalm down the row over the end of the
OL,14,Fwinter fuel allowance. But, by the
OL,15,Fsame token, why should well-off
OL,16,Fretired people pay nothing?
OL,18,FCould more government money for
OL,19,Foverseas services relieve pressure on
OL,20,FBBC finances without asking the public
OL,21,Fto pay more?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/12
