OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FAll those issues are worth debating.
OL,8,FAhead of Charter Renewal, there needs
OL,9,Fto be a proper debate about the scope
OL,10,Fof BBC programmes and services.
OL,12,FNobody who believes the BBC should be
OL,13,Fat the centre of national life would
OL,14,Fargue that popular programmes,
OL,15,Fmainstream drama and light
OL,16,Fentertainment are not important.
OL,18,FIf the BBC only served minorities or
OL,19,Fmade programmes which were self-
OL,20,Fconsciously serious or distinctive, it
OL,21,Fwould have no right to claim funding
OL,22,Ffrom every household.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G10/12
