OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FBut are there areas for improvement?
OL,7,FThings like quiz shows with large cash
OL,8,Fprizes which ` however well made `
OL,9,Freally belong elsewhere?
OL,11,FIs Radio 2 too similar to commercial
OL,12,Fradio, stripped of much of the live
OL,13,Fand evening specialist music which
OL,14,Fonce made it stand out?
OL,16,FSimilarly so, say, children's
OL,17,Fprogrammes and demanding drama like
OL,18,FWolf Hall need bolstered.
OL,20,FIn other words, is the balance right
OL,21,Feven where most individual programmes
OL,22,Fare fine?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G11/12
