OL,3,CTV Licence increase: a welcome boost
OL,4,Cfor public service broadcasting
OL,6,FSupporters of the BBC should never be
OL,7,Fafraid of debates on practical
OL,8,Falternatives to the TV Licence or the
OL,9,Fkind of programmes and services it
OL,10,Fshould be spent on.
OL,12,FBut for now they should just feel
OL,13,Frelieved that those with a dogmatic or
OL,14,Fideological hostility to the
OL,15,Fcorporation will not be able to
OL,16,Fattempt to undermine an important part
OL,17,Fof Britain's culture and society.
